author: @josephprovencher6345
content: Nick, I never hit a play button so fast to one of your videos as I have seeing that you were at this historic event! I'm so extremely happy for you. I've been a diehard Madonna fan for almost 40 years and everytime I'd get the chance to see her live, something would happen so I couldn't go until this tour. My little sister actually surprised me with tickets and we both got to experience her live in Boston Massachusetts on January 9th, 2024. It was a dream come true and she did NOT dissapoint. I was BEYOND thrilled that she performed Crazy For You which is my favorite song of all time. Bob The Drag Queen was amazing too and so happy he was a part of the show ‚ù§üéâ
